%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Immortal Defender:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^ %^RESET%^ Level 20 Base Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^ %^RESET%^ Counter (WeaponAndShield Feat)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
 %^RESET%^L1: defenders presence
 %^RESET%^L4: shield charge
 %^RESET%^L7: shield master

%^RESET%^And immortal defender is the master of fighting with a weaponand shield. They are the immovable front line of any fighting force. A first level immortal defender is able to activate a defenders presencewhich will bolster allies in battle, giving them extra vitality to shrug off enemy attacks. Once the immortal defender reaches level four, they are able to use a devestating shield charge that will knock attackers scattering and can even be used to charge through an enemy lines, making room for all who are following the immortal defender in their wake. Finally, upon reaching level seven, an immortal defender becomes a masterwith their shield. They are highly resistant to being knocked down while using their shield. The immortal defender also will not loose his melee attacks while he is fully defensive using shieldwall.

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^feats, skills, styles, mystyle, spells, cast, prepare